      propertyPath: m_text
      value: <b>Saruman the White</b> stands in the majesty of Orthanc, chief of
        the Istari, master of lore, ring-craft, and the long devices of the Wise.
        His voice is a weapon finer than steel, entering the counsels of kings and
        bending proud hearts with honeyed reason until obedience seems wisdom and
        surrender seems peace.<br><br>This variant favors influence, manipulation,
        and command exercised with polished restraint.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
