    - target: {fileID: 2803997602101439279, guid: c3bd549b2bc2114499e34484479a96ff, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: <b>Saruman</b> is the master of Orthanc, once the chief of the wise,
        now the architect of his own dominion.His voice bends courts, his mind measures
        every weakness, and his ambition refuses to wait for permission. He builds
        in silence, gathering strength behind fair words, and he intends to remake
        the world in the image of his will.<br><br>His design begins with a careful
        reach into the courts of Rohan, the securing of a pliant voice, and the quiet
        unearthing of power long buried. From Orthanc he turns influence into force
        and raises the first ranks of his war.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
